==Deployments== 
* 29 July 2011- 27 February 2012
* 20 March 2014- 20 October 2014

==In popular culture==
''Wayne E. Meyer'' was featured on the "Destroyer Disaster" episode of the [[Food Network]] show ''[[Dinner: Impossible]]'' .<ref>[http://www.foodnetwork.com/dinner-impossible/destroyer-disaster/index.html]</ref>

